lines.text: In this business you gotta have smarts.
I'm so rich I own my own S-and-L.
A gambler has a death wish - tonight I'm betting my whole future on you, and I don't wanna come up snake eyes.
You and old what's-his-name ride the bucking bronco last night?
Keep an eye on that long-haired punk over there.
I killed a lot of gooks in Nam just like you.
Did that cowboy make it with you yet?
This chocolate popsicle will melt in your mouth.
